===Etymology===
From {{etyl|it|en}} {{term|alla cappella||lang=it|in the manner of the [Sistine] chapel}}, referring to non-instrumental choirs; from Latin ''[[a-]]'', ''[[ad]]'', "to", + ''[[cappella]]'', "chapel".

